'''1,2-二氟乙烷'''是一种[[氢氟烃|氢氟烃]]，每个碳原子都连接着一个氟原子，[[示性式|示性式]]CH<sub>2</sub>FCH<sub>2</sub>F。它是[[1,1-二氟乙烷|1,1-二氟乙烷]]的异构体。它的HFC名称是'''HFC-152'''，没有字母后缀。<ref name=nappa>{{cite journal|last1=Nappa|first1=Mario J.|last2=Sievert|first2=Allen C.|title=The chlorination of 1,2-difluoroethane (HFC-152)|journal=Journal of Fluorine Chemistry|date=June 1993|volume=62|issue=2–3|pages=111–118|doi=10.1016/S0022-1139(00)80085-8}}</ref>当冷却到低温时，它可以具有不同的构象，顺式和反式结构。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Huber-Wälchli|first1=P.|last2=Günthard|first2=Hs.H.|title=Trapping of unstable conformations from thermal molecular beams in argon matrices: 1,2-difluoroethane and 1,3-butadiene, i.r. spectra and conformer equilibria|journal=Spectrochimica Acta Part A: Molecular Spectroscopy|date=January 1981|volume=37|issue=5|pages=285–304|doi=10.1016/0584-8539(81)80159-6|bibcode=1981AcSpA..37..285H}}</ref>在液态时，1,2-二氟乙烷的两种异构体的数量相等，容易相互转化。在气态时的1,2-二氟乙烷分子通常为顺式结构。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Klaboe|first1=Peter|last2=Nielsen|first2=J. Rud|title=Infrared and Raman Spectra of Fluorinated Ethanes. XIII. 1,2-Difluoroethane|journal=The Journal of Chemical Physics|date=1960|volume=33|issue=6|pages=1764|doi=10.1063/1.1731499|bibcode=1960JChPh..33.1764K}}</ref>

它的编号HFC-152的意思如下：2代表有两个氟原子，5代表5-1，也就是四个氢原子，而1则代表1+1，也就是两个碳原子。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Kirk|first1=Raymond E.|last2=Othmer|first2=Donald F.|last3=Grayson|first3=Martin|title=Kirk-Othmer Encyclopedia of Chemical Technology|volume=11|page=282|edition=4}}</ref>

==形成==
[[乙烯|乙烯]]会和氟气进行爆炸性反应，形成1,2-二氟乙烷和[[氟乙烯|氟乙烯]]的混合物。当被[[近红外线|近红外线]]照射时，乙烯会和氟固体反应，生成1,2-二氟乙烷。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Hauge|first1=R. H.|last2=Gransden|first2=S.|last3=Wang|first3=J. L. F.|last4=Margrave|first4=J. L.|title=Studies of the reactions of molecular fluorine with methane, acetylene, ethylene, allene, and other small hydrocarbons in matrices at low temperatures|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=November 1979|volume=101|issue=23|pages=6950–6954|doi=10.1021/ja00517a027}}</ref>

==反应==
CH<sub>2</sub>FCH<sub>2</sub>F在光照下和氯气反应。反应会形成两种物质—CH<sub>2</sub>FCCl<sub>2</sub>F和CHClFCHClF。这两种化合物的比例取决于溶剂。<ref name=nappa/>

